  <note type="content" displayLabel="Note">This collection includes materials accessioned as 4700.0335; A digital version of the transcript (pdf) exists for duplication purposes; A digital version of the audio recording (mp3) exists for duplication purposes and public access in the Special Collections Reading Room; Interview conducted by Maxine Crump.</note>
  <note type="biographical/historical" displayLabel="Biographical Note">Freya Rivers was an LSU alumna and a party to the LSU desegregation suit.</note>
